PX4 Secure Boot Chain

graph TD
A[Boot ROM] --> B[First-stage Bootloader]
B -->|Verify Signature| C[PX4 Firmware]
C --> D[PX4 Modules]
D --> E[Flight Tasks]

ArduPilot Data Flow & Trust Boundaries

graph LR
GCS[Ground Control Station] -->|MAVLink| FC[Flight Controller]
FC --> S[Sensor Fusion]
S --> N[Navigation]
N --> A[Actuators]
