N
A
end

MAVLink Threat Surface (Defensive View)

graph LR
GCS -->|Signed MAVLink| FC
Attacker -.->|Unsigned / Replay| FC
FC -->|Reject & Log| LOGS[Security Logs]

Simulation vs Real-World Isolation

graph TD
SIM[Simulation Environment] -->|Virtual Links| SITL[SITL Autopilot]
SITL --> LOGS
REAL[Real Hardware] -.->|Physically Isolated| SIM


