ğŸ†š PX4 vs ArduPilot Security Comparison

Area	PX4	ArduPilot

RTOS	NuttX	ChibiOS / RTOS Abstraction
Secure Boot	Supported (board-dependent)	Limited / board-dependent
Firmware Signing	Supported	Partial support
MAVLink Signing	Supported	Supported
Failsafes	Strong modular failsafes	Extensive configurable failsafes
SITL Maturity	Very high	Very high



